{"title": "I made an free unlimited captcha alternative", "link": "https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48343112", "summary": "<p>I made an unlimited free captcha service.\nI used altcha before, but it only focuses on Pow which was kind of hard to figure out bots.\nSo,I made this service. It tests Pow+11 more stuff on your browser and updates every 10 minuites to stop new bots, is light, and easy to use! Maybe you should consider using this?\nThere's a test for this: sh.krl.kr/test\nHope this is great for you!\nWebsite: sh.krl.kr</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Comments URL: <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48343112\">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48343112</a></p>\n<p>Points: 2</p>\n<p># Comments: 1</p>", "published": "2026-05-31T04:48:18+00:00", "source": "Hacker News Best", "category": "techblog", "matched_entities": {}, "ontology": {"repo": "BlogRadar", "category": "techblog", "ontology_version": "0.1.0", "source_event_model": "blog_post", "event_model_id": "tech.blog_post", "evidence_policy_ids": ["source_metadata", "article_text"], "event_model_payload": {"headline": "I made an free unlimited captcha alternative", "source_name": "Hacker News Best", "source_url": "https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48343112", "published_at": "2026-05-31T04:48:18+00:00", "summary": "<p>I made an unlimited free captcha service.\nI used altcha before, but it only focuses on Pow which was kind of hard to figure out bots.\nSo,I made this service. It tests Pow+11 more stuff on your browser and updates every 10 minuites to stop new bots, is light, and easy to use! Maybe you should consider using this?\nThere's a test for this: sh.krl.kr/test\nHope this is great for you!\nWebsite: sh.krl.kr</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Comments URL: <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48343112\">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48343112</a></p>\n<p>Points: 2</p>\n<p># Comments: 1</p>"}}, "logged_at": "2026-05-31T05:18:42.178473+00:00"}
